---
title: Sesame Pork Schnitzel & Garlic Potatoes with BBQ-Sriracha Sauce & Apple Slaw
description: It’s a twist on pork schnitzel, we’re combining sriracha with BBQ sauce so the schnitzels are extra mouth-watering when this sauce is drizzled over. This dish becomes more alluring when you catch the scent of garlic-infused potato, crushed so that you can’t miss them on the plate.
